## Problem 2 — Find Minimum

```python
def find_min(arr, i=0):
    if i == len(arr) - 1:
        return arr[i]
    min_of_rest = find_min(arr, i+1)
    if arr[i] < min_of_rest:
        return arr[i]
    return min_of_rest
```

Time : O(n) | Space : O(n)

Mistake I made — wrote return 1 in base case instead of
return arr[i]. Never hardcode base case values.

