## Problem 3 — Find Maximum

```python
def find_max(arr, i=0):
    if i == len(arr) - 1:
        return arr[i]
    max_of_rest = find_max(arr, i+1)
    if arr[i] > max_of_rest:
        return arr[i]
    return max_of_rest
```

Time : O(n) | Space : O(n)

Same as find_min. Only the condition changes from < to >.

